cyclone.name: ETA
cyclone.current_location: about 90 miles north of the western tip of Cuba
cyclone.trajectory: moving north to north-northeast, expected to run parallel to but just offshore the west coast of Florida, then turn northeast toward Apalachee Bay late Thursday into Friday
